<h5><a href="x90544.xml">Bachelors of Science in Nursing (RN to BSN)</a></h5>
<p>A Baccalaureate of Science Degree in Nursing permits the graduate to be hired for a larger variety of nursing jobs. A student must have a valid RN license to apply for this program at BYU-Idaho.</p>
<h3><a href="x90641.xml">Family Nursing, Life Skills (for non-nursing majors)</a></h3>
